             were indicted for <rs id="t18190113-75-off430" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18190113-75-off430" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18190113-75-off430" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18190113-75-cd431" type="crimeDate">8th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190113-75-off430 t18190113-75-cd431"></join>, 5 lbs. of lead, value 1 s. 6 d., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18190113-75-victim721" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Wilson
                        <interp inst="t18190113-75-victim721" type="surname" value="Wilson"></interp>
